body.description: Our first aid restock kit replaces the commonly used items in OSHA and ANSI compliant first aid kits. The medSoft first aid kit refill comes jam-packed with the following items: 200 Piece First Aid Kit College: Absorbent Adhesive Dressing, large (2), Absorbent Adhesive Dressing, medium (2), Absorbent Adhesive Dressing, small (2), Adhesive Bandage, standard size (30), Adhesive Bandage, small size (30), Adhesive Eye Pad (4), Adhesive Spot Bandage (16), Prep Wipes (8), Disinfectant Wipes (8), Butterfly Wound Closure Bandages (16), Cold Compress, Disposable (1), Cotton tip applicator (16), CPR Facemask (1), Crease Bandage (2), Dressing Pad, large (2), Dressing Pad, medium (2), Dressing Pad, small (4), Emergency Blanket (1), Fingertip Bandages (14), First Aid Gloves, Disposable (2), Knuckle Bandages (10), Medical Tape, 2.5cm x 5m (2), Metal Scissors (1), PBT Elastic Bandage, large (2), PBT Elastic Bandage, medium (2), Safety Pins (12), Sterile Gauze Pad (6), Triangular Bandage (1). Your purchase of your first aid kit for dorm rooms is insured with a 1-year warranty money back guarantee: All first aid kits for college students by MedSoft come with a 1-year no questions asked money back guarantee! Our first aid kit refill makes sure you always have the most commonly worn out first aid items on hand, with 200 pieces of medical supplies. Pick up your first aid kit camping today, and be prepared for any situation. Our first aid kit travel pack comes handy wherever you go. This first aid kit refill contains a full supply pack, so be sure to always be prepared for any situation wherever you go.
